thread.title: BRIEF-Fermiere Du Casino Municipal Cannes FY net profit up at 29.4 million euros

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Fermiere Du Casino Municipal Cannes FY net profit up at 29.4 million euros

organizations.name: brief-fermiere du casino municipal cannes fy

text:
Jan 12 (Reuters) - FERMIERE DU CASINO MUNICIPAL CANNES SA :
* FY REVENUE EUR 140.9 MILLION VERSUS EUR 142.1 MILLION YEAR AGO
* FY OPERATING PROFIT EUR 22.4 MILLION VERSUS EUR 24.7 MILLION YEAR AGO
* FY NET PROFIT GROUP SHARE EUR 29.4 MILLION VERSUS EUR 15.2 MILLION YEAR AGO Source text : bit.ly/2ASOInI Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
